      <title>印度新任央行行长立场鸽派，印度债券或将上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/bonds-may-gain-on-rate-cut-bets-after-india-names-new-rbi-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在印度政府任命职业官僚桑杰马洛特拉 (Sanjay Malhotra) 为新任印度储备银行行长后，分析师押注印度将采取更为宽松的货币政策，印度债券有望上涨，而卢比将走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/bonds-may-gain-on-rate-cut-bets-after-india-names-new-rbi-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 03:28:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
