    <item>
      <title>受严重干旱影响，Volcafe 下调巴西阿拉比卡咖啡产量预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/volcafe-slashes-brazil-arabica-coffee-outlook-on-severe-drought</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Volcafe Ltd. 是全球最大的咖啡贸易商之一，在对巴西阿拉比卡咖啡产区进行农作物巡查后发现该地区长期遭受干旱的严重影响，该公司下调了对巴西阿拉比卡咖啡产量的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/volcafe-slashes-brazil-arabica-coffee-outlook-on-severe-drought</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 22:46:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：随着美国 CPI 数据公布，中国经济放缓，股市回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国最新刺激计划的推动力逐渐消退，且交易员等待本周晚些时候公布的美国关键通胀数据，全球股市周二下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 22:30:18 GMT</pubDate>
